  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/2215199b3f9e66f5f09cbb3f7cc79025.poster.avif?t=1741046483\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/2215199b3f9e66f5f09cbb3f7cc79025.webm?t=1741046483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/2215199b3f9e66f5f09cbb3f7cc79025.mp4?t=1741046483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...A knight who has lost his memory and body embarks on a quest to rediscover his heart...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>【Story】</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join a knight, whose essence is within his armor, as he sets off on a journey of memories with a cat that resides within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why did he forget his heart? Why is his form only armor? Who are the people he encounters along the way?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the knight regains his memories, his journey will become truly unforgettable...<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/8ef13db075bd4c999d051e55767c8975.poster.avif?t=1741046483\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/8ef13db075bd4c999d051e55767c8975.webm?t=1741046483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/8ef13db075bd4c999d051e55767c8975.mp4?t=1741046483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>【Battle】</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill of intense battles, where you can shatter your foes into pieces!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in exhilarating combat unlike any other, with over 150 unique enemies to defeat using a variety of skills, from powerful magic to masterful swordsmanship!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a vast map brimming with dungeons, towns, treasure chests, and formidable adversaries!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/235dea0b694de6ea2abf6198227a5ca7.poster.avif?t=1741046483\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/235dea0b694de6ea2abf6198227a5ca7.webm?t=1741046483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/235dea0b694de6ea2abf6198227a5ca7.mp4?t=1741046483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>【Additional Features】</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect over 300 types of equipment and items to enhance your power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into endless exploration and gameplay with Black Crystals, consecutive battles, and training grounds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[material]<br>Music：ユーフルカ様 <br>SE：効果音ラボ様 <br>character：エトリエ様 <br>Momster：qut様 <br>Effects：ぴぽや様 <br>Icon：猫屋様 <br>Map：ねくら様 <br>Event：誰そ彼亭様 <br>Item：Un Almacen  からし様 <br>Menu：CLOSET様</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/2215199b3f9e66f5f09cbb3f7cc79025.poster.avif?t=1741046483\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/2215199b3f9e66f5f09cbb3f7cc79025.webm?t=1741046483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/2215199b3f9e66f5f09cbb3f7cc79025.mp4?t=1741046483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...A knight who has lost his memory and body embarks on a quest to rediscover his heart...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>【Story】</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join a knight, whose essence is within his armor, as he sets off on a journey of memories with a cat that resides within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why did he forget his heart? Why is his form only armor? Who are the people he encounters along the way?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the knight regains his memories, his journey will become truly unforgettable...<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/8ef13db075bd4c999d051e55767c8975.poster.avif?t=1741046483\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/8ef13db075bd4c999d051e55767c8975.webm?t=1741046483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/8ef13db075bd4c999d051e55767c8975.mp4?t=1741046483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>【Battle】</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill of intense battles, where you can shatter your foes into pieces!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in exhilarating combat unlike any other, with over 150 unique enemies to defeat using a variety of skills, from powerful magic to masterful swordsmanship!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a vast map brimming with dungeons, towns, treasure chests, and formidable adversaries!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/235dea0b694de6ea2abf6198227a5ca7.poster.avif?t=1741046483\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/235dea0b694de6ea2abf6198227a5ca7.webm?t=1741046483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025100/extras/235dea0b694de6ea2abf6198227a5ca7.mp4?t=1741046483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>【Additional Features】</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect over 300 types of equipment and items to enhance your power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into endless exploration and gameplay with Black Crystals, consecutive battles, and training grounds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[material]<br>Music：ユーフルカ様 <br>SE：効果音ラボ様 <br>character：エトリエ様 <br>Momster：qut様 <br>Effects：ぴぽや様 <br>Icon：猫屋様 <br>Map：ねくら様 <br>Event：誰そ彼亭様 <br>Item：Un Almacen  からし様 <br>Menu：CLOSET様</p>",
